Class StatsRole

java.lang.Object
it.unipd.dei.webapp.lupus.resource.AbstractResource
it.unipd.dei.webapp.lupus.resource.StatsRole
All Implemented Interfaces:
Resource
public class StatsRole extends AbstractResource
Represents statistics about a role. This class contains information about the role's name, the number of times it appears, and the number of wins associated with it.
Since:
1.0
Version:
1.0
